value: Resident, swamps and other wetlands: all S of Sahara except arid NE and SW, N Kenya and most of Uganda.
Aquatic habitats of Africa south of the Sahara
papyrus swamps, reedbeds, marshes with rushes & open water, ponds with water-lilies, floodplains & pans w.emergent grass or sedge;flooded farmland, sewage ponds;lowlands to 2000m
